Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.37,1:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的朋友卡普，在陷害勒索麦克雷\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You and you friend Karp were settin' up McRyan for blackmail,
