Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.21,1:07:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么做的？告诉他说桥下流水会刺激你兴奋？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you do? You tell him running water under a well-lit bridge gets you hot?
