Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.48,1:08:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但我可不会消失，我告诉你  - 是吗，我会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- But I'm not disappearin'. I'll tell you that. - Yeah? I am.
