Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.27,1:08:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 曼尼不会让我受伤害的  - 不就是他让你上车的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Manny wouldn't get me hurt. - Didn't he get you into the car?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.62,1:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，但他并不知道…  - 他不知道轮胎会被射爆，他一无所知\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, but he didn't know... - He didn't know the tyre'd be shot out. He didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.08,1:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他不可能知道  - 算了吧，莎莉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- He couldn't have. - Come on, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.11,1:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我在那里拉你出来，你现在已经死了，还不明白吗\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If I hadn't been there to pull you out of the river, you'd be dead now. Don't you get it?
