Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.66,1:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，丈夫、市政官员，大多数是小地方来的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know. Husbands, city officials, mostly small-town guys.
