Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.09,1:09:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我不用真的做什么事，比如跟他们搞\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know I didn't really have to do anything like screw 'em or anything.
