Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.14,1:09:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我只是愿意去这么想，这样会容易些\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I guess I wanted to believe it. It just made it easier.
