Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.58,1:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，谁雇了曼尼去拍照？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. Who hired Manny to take these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.78,1:09:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know.
