Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.52,1:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试去拿片子，然后你能不能放过我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'll try and get the film. Then will you just leave me alone about all this?
