Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.84,1:12:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，6千对于这种活计可是一大笔钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I mean, six grand-- that's a lotta money for this kind of a job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.05,1:12:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 要我说他的钱物有所值  - 他本不应该死的，老天在上\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I'd say he got his money's worth. - He wasn't supposed to die, for chrise sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.76,1:12:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来连受伤都不会，那是个意外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He wasn't even supposed to get hurt. That was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.07,1:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，我后来琢磨出来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know. I figured it out later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.27,1:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个疯狂的点子…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This nut's idea was
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.67,1:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是射爆麦克雷的车胎，导致一场小事故\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}was to shoot out the tyre of McRyan's car, cause a little crackup.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.40,1:13:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 警察出现，他们把他拖出车子…  - 还有我？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- The police show up, they pull him outta the car... - With me?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.78,1:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对，还有你，然后我全拍下来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, yeah, with you. And I'd get it all on film.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.91,1:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事故\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Some little crackup.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.16,1:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来不会死的，那是个意外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He wasn't supposed to die. That car was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.93,1:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得告诉你多少遍？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How many times I gotta tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.71,1:13:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼尼，咱们害死了他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Manny, we got him killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.42,1:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，等等，咱们？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, hey, wait. We?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.38,1:13:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“咱们”是什么意思？咱们什么也没干\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you mean, we, huh? We didn't do nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.68,1:13:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在树林子里，你在车里，我没射轮胎，你也没有\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I was in the woods, you were in the car. I didn't shoot out no tyre. You didn't neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.22,1:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，拜托别跟我来道德良心这一套\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, please, don't give me none of this conscience shit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.85,1:13:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了，事情弄成这样也没人为此而哭\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Besides, nobody is exactly cryin' over the way things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.03,1:13:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那家伙活着会发生什么事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What would've happened if the guy had lived?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.82,1:13:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事业就毁了，拜我们所赐\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His career was finished, thanks to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.66,1:13:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种结果对那家伙倒好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This way the guy comes out ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.08,1:13:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他成了圣人，烈士\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a saint, a martyr.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.08,1:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天，今早他们还通过了他的一个议案\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Christ, they passed one of his bills this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.71,1:13:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是头猪，曼尼\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You're a pig, Manny.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.04,1:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也是头猪  - 什么猪不猪的鬼话？你这是怎么回事？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- And I'm a pig too. - What the hell is with this 'pig' shit? What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得说出真相，否则就结案了，残局要被收拾了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We gotta tell the truth before the books are closed and the loose ends are cut off.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.35,1:14:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.06,1:14:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克雷是被谋杀的，大家应该知道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}McRyan was murdered and everybody should know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.39,1:14:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了？咱们害死了他，你想坐牢吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Are you crazy? We got him killed. Do you wanna go to jail?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.83,1:14:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，可当时我在车里，你在树林里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, but I was in the car and you were in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.61,1:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为会有人相信吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You think anybody is gonna believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.32,1:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，但我必须做点什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know but I gotta do somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.45,1:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，比如闭上嘴，拿钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, like just keep your mouth shut and take the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.33,1:14:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，宝贝听着，这是扎普顿影片{\fs12}肯尼迪遇刺影片{\r}之后最大的事情\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, babe, listen. This is the biggest thing since the Zapruder film.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.29,1:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不管  - 这事更大\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I don't care. - It's bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.46,1:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是历史事件，姑娘\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is history we got here, girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.59,1:14:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会成为一大笔财富\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This is gonna be a goddam fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.84,1:14:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会登上每一家报纸，会登上每一家杂志\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's gonna be in every newspaper. It's gonna be in every magazine.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.64,1:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在他妈的“六点钟”新闻播出\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's gonna be on the fuckin' six o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.60,1:14:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会围绕这事制作电视特辑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're gonna build TV specials around this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.31,1:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会为此大捞一笔\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And they're gonna ask a goddam fortune for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.52,1:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你不明白吗宝贝？咱们发了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey. Don't you understand, sweetheart? We're set.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.15,1:15:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管，曼尼，我不要沾这件事的边\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't care, Manny. I don't want any part of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.55,1:15:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以留着那事后3千\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You can keep your three after.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.03,1:15:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，别这么傻了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, don't be such a dope, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.28,1:15:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱就是钱\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Money's money.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.87,1:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就像是两只秃鹫\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We sound like a couple of vultures.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.29,1:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪，秃鹫…你是吞了一整箱动物饼干吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pigs, vultures... You swallow a whole box of animal crackers?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.51,1:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要喝一点，曼尼，给我一杯酒\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I need a drink, Manny. Come on, give me a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.93,1:15:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好，当然，咱们喝一杯  - 瓶子给我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, sure I'll get us a drink. - Just give me the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.27,1:15:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，你在动脑筋了，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, now you're thinkin', babe.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.85,1:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许咱们可以去亚特兰大城  - 我不喜欢亚特兰大城\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- We'll go over to Atlantic City maybe. - I don't like Atlantic City.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.70,1:15:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不喜欢？我会带你四处转转  - 住手，不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- No? I'll show you around. - Stop. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.45,1:15:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们会有很多美好时光  - 曼尼，住手\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- We'll have a lot of good times. - Manny, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.49,1:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 宝贝，我们会开心大笑  - 拜托，曼尼，不要\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Sweatheart, We'll have a lotta laughs. - Please, Manny, don't. Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.29,1:16:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼尼，求你，求你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Manny, please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.50,1:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松，宝贝\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Relax, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.00,1:16:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Fantastic. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.71,1:16:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.51,1:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 如何？现在怎么办？  - 你太棒了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Well? Now what? - You're great.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.18,1:16:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给那个电视记者打电话，我们要广播出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna call that TV guy. We're gonna get it on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.76,1:16:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我给你做些吃的吧？  - 好，这样不错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Can I make you somethin' to eat? - Yeah, that'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.56,1:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 玉米片怎么样？  - 都行\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- How about some cornflakes? - Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.40,1:17:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请找弗兰克·唐纳休，我是杰克·泰瑞\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Frank Donahue, please. It's Jack Terry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.70,1:17:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂  - 唐纳休先生，杰克·泰瑞的电话，请稍候\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah? - Mr. Donahue, Jack Terry calling. One moment please.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.60,1:17:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 唐纳休先生  - 杰克，什么事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Mr Donahue? - Jack. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.95,1:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着，我改主意了，我要你听听那带子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, I've changed my mind. I want you to hear that tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.96,1:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还拿到了整卷卡普的胶片\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've also got the whole Karp's oraginal film.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.88,1:17:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把它们放在一起，任何人都看得出那不是意外\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you run 'em together, anyone can see it wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.11,1:17:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，杰克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's great, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.41,1:17:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不能说，能不能20分钟后给你打回去？你号码多少？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look, I can't talk now. Can I get back to you in 20 minutes? What's your number?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.98,1:17:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.88,1:17:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要我干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She wanted me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.30,1:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她要求的，她求我做，那个婊子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She asked for it. She begged me for it, the bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.97,1:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不想干\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I... I didn't wanna do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.31,1:17:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She made me do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.77,1:17:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问她，她会告诉你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You ask her. She'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.56,1:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧，她在哪？  - 我不知道，某个地方\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- OK. Where is she? - I don't know. Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.32,1:17:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个大洞里，靠近雷丁市场，那里正在搞建筑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}In that big hole, near the Reading Market, where they're buildin' somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.66,1:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要听她的，她让我干的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But don't listen to her. She made me do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.79,1:18:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，告诉我你在哪儿\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK. Just tell me where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.25,1:18:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Where...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.33,1:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着，杰克\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Listen, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.23,1:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道，这东西没有意义，除非你来上电视\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You realise this won't mean a thing unless you come on the air...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.88,1:18:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说是你看见和听见的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...and you say it's what you saw and heard?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.22,1:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会说是我听见的  - 好，太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I'll say it's what I heard. - OK. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.72,1:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，那女孩怎么样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Jack, what about that girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.12,1:18:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在场，她一定听见了，我们能让她来吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}She was there. She must have heard it. Can we get her on?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.77,1:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你看，她是在场，但别牵扯她，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No. Look, she did, but don't involve her, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.35,1:18:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 干嘛不？  - 因为她…她并不认可自己的行为\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Why not? - Well, because she just...She's not exactly proud of what she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.98,1:18:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，没问题，杰克，不过…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK. No problem, Jack. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.38,1:18:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我跟她谈谈？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}could I at least talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.78,1:18:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这个就看她了  - 好，我会处理的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Well, that's up to her. I... - OK. Look, I'll take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.50,1:18:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，你能不能等一下？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Jack, could you hold on just one second?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.70,1:18:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 杰克，咱们何时见？我何时能看到东西？  - 随时\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Jack, when can we get together? When can I see this stuff? - Uh, any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.37,1:18:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了，我下午能否给你电话？哪儿能找到你？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Great. Can I give you a call this afternoon? Where can I reach you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.09,1:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我整天在家  - 好，我到时打电话，再见\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I'll be home all day. - OK. I'll call you then. So long.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.47,1:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，你好吗？  - 听着，我刚跟唐纳休打过电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Oh, hi. How're you doing? - Listen, I just spoke to Donahue.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.97,1:19:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是谁？ - 你知道的，一个电视记者，只做调查新闻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Who's he? - You know, a TV newsman. Does investigative pieaces.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.47,1:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，对我没意义，我不看新闻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, it doesn't mean anything to me. I don't watch the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.81,1:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.77,1:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想干嘛？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What's he wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.07,1:19:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，他说他要播出去\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, he said he'd put it on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.73,1:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他待会儿给我打电话安排会面  - 太好了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- He'd call later and set up a meeting. - That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.31,1:19:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还说想要我上电视，说那是我所见所闻\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He also said he'd like me to go on TV and say that it's what I saw and heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.19,1:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不这样做带子就没有用处\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Said the tape wouldn't be any good without it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.93,1:19:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他也想让你上电视\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}But he'd also like you to go on too.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.03,1:19:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不，算了，我不想参与此事\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, no. Forget it, I don't want any part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.74,1:19:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不想被牵连，但至少你能否跟他谈谈？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, I know you don't wanna get involved, but would you at least speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.31,1:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不想\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.62,1:19:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，莎莉，他们不可能说咱俩都听岔了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Sally. They can't say we're both hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.75,1:19:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们公开此事，就没人能伤害我们了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If we get this out in the open, there's no one that can hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.51,1:19:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，我考虑一下好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right, look, I'll think about it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.97,1:19:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早在市政厅，费城警方总警监麦基召开了记者招待会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}At City Hall this morning, Chief Inspector Mackey at Philadelphia police held a news conference.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.18,1:19:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说对麦克雷州长之死的初步调查…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He said a preliminary investigation into Governor McRyan's death...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.81,1:19:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭示出他是一场怪异的意外事故受害者\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...revealed that he was the victim of a freak accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.64,1:19:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 胡扯  - 今天其它新闻…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Bullshit. - Also in the news today...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.27,1:19:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于玛丽·罗伯特的离奇色情凶杀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...is the bizarre sex killing of Mary Robert,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.69,1:19:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自中央城区的22岁女招待\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}a 22-year-old receptionist from the Center City area.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.28,1:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的尸体上午十点在雷丁车站施工现场被发现\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Her body was found at 10 a.m. in the Reading Terminal excavation site...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.32,1:20:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前警方接到一个匿名电话爆料\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...after police received a tip from an anonymous caller.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.92,1:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩先是被掐脖子\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The girl had been strangled,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.67,1:20:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后其腹部及腹股沟被利器反复戳刺\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}then repeatedly stabbed with a pointed instrument across her stomach and groin.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.01,1:20:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺伤形成一个自由钟的形状\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The stab marks were in the pattern of a Liberty Bell.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.27,1:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方无法解释此怪异伤残\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The police are at a loss to explain this grotesque mutilation.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.10,1:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们询问了法医心理学家约瑟夫·福克斯博士\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We asked forensic psychologist Dr Joseph Fuchs...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.65,1:20:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个自由钟形状的伤口可能会跟…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...what connection there might be between the bell-shaped wounds...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.32,1:20:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将来到的自由日庆典有关吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...and the upcoming Liberty Day celebration.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.74,1:20:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂，我是莎莉  - 嗨，莎莉，我是弗兰克·唐纳休\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Hi. This is Sally. - Hi, Sally. Frank Donahue here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.78,1:20:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，你应该给杰克打电话的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, you were supposed to call Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.81,1:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，你看，这事太操蛋了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yes, you know, Sally, It's the damnedest thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.11,1:20:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法电话联系杰克安排会面\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I can't get Jack on the phone to arrange a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.62,1:20:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的电话整天占线，所以，我就想着给你打一个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}His line's been busy all day. So I thought I'd give you a ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.08,1:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，怎样？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah? So?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.56,1:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话出问题了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Something's wrong with your phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.53,1:21:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整天试着给你打电话，总是听到忙音\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been trying to call you all day. I kept gettin' a busy signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.32,1:21:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.12,1:21:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一下午都在这儿，一直在等唐纳休的电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been here all afternoon, I've been waitin' for Donahue's call.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.40,1:21:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦对，他也在给你打电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, yeah, he's been trying to call you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.91,1:21:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但他听到忙音  - 你怎么知道的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- But he was gettin' a busy signal. - How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.28,1:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打给我，他要我5点钟去30街车站见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He called me. He wants me to meet him at 30th Street Station at five.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.45,1:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么有你的号码？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}How did he get your number?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.99,1:21:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是你给他的吗？  - 不是\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Didn't you give it to him? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.08,1:21:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何区别？记者总有办法弄到电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, what diferences made? Reporters have a way of gettin' numbers.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.96,1:21:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见他，给他录音带和胶片，就没事了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So I wanna meet him. I'll give him the tape and the film and that'll be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.46,1:21:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你要给他带子？他怎么没给我回电话？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you mean? You're gonna give him the tape? Why didn't he call me back?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.88,1:21:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想单独见我，他试图说服我上电视\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He wants to meet with me alone, he's trying to talk me into goin' on the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.93,1:21:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，他本该给我回电话的，这事不对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, he should've called me back. This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.14,1:21:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的电话出故障了  - 我的电话没故障\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Your phone is out of order. - My phone is not out of order.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.14,1:21:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整天在这里，我打过一个电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been here all day. I made a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.77,1:21:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给，你听\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.77,1:21:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许电话公司也参与阴谋了  - 不，事情不对头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Maybe the phone company's in on the conspiracy too. - No, something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.31,1:21:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这有什么区别\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I mean what diference does it made?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.61,1:22:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们去见他，我给他录音带和胶片，就此了结\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Let's just meet him. I'll give him the tape and the film and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.69,1:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦他拿到胶片，事情就结束了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Once he's got the film, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.07,1:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，他想要见你，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All right. He wants to meet you, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.16,1:22:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对  - 好，你得去，你得见他\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah. - OK. You're gonna go and you're gonna meet him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.75,1:22:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他说话没问题，你就给他胶片和录音带\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, if he sounds OK, you'll give him the film and tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.54,1:22:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要去哪？- 附近\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Where are you gonna be? - Close.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.04,1:22:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.88,1:22:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你连线\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna wire you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.25,1:22:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我连线？为什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Wire me? What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.17,1:22:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做好所有基础工作，这回没人能耍我\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I'm gonna cover all the bases. Nobody's gonna fuck me this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.35,1:22:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样要是他拿到胶片就消失\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}This way, if he disappears with the film
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.55,1:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没法假装没拿到，因为我都录下来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}he can't pretend he didn't take it cos I got him on tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.64,1:22:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有点妄想症了？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Aren't you gettin' a little paranoid here?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.60,1:22:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是媒体人，这是大新闻，他干嘛不播出去？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He's a newsman. This is a very big story. Why isn't he gonna put it on the air?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.61,1:22:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我交给警方以后怎么样，他们洗掉了它，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Look what happened when I took it to the police. They erased it, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.03,1:22:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在干嘛？  - 我在做一份拷贝，为咱们自己留条后路没坏处\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- What are you doin'? - I'm making a copy, there's nothing wrong to cover ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.32,1:22:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？那胶片怎么办？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah? Well, what about the film?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.28,1:22:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶片怎么办？我现在没法拷贝，没时间做\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What about the film?I can't make a copy now. I don't have time to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.50,1:22:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧好吧，连上线吧  - 脱掉外衣\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- OK, OK. Bring on the wire. - Take off your coat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.42,1:22:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，咱们赶紧弄完\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK. Let's get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.10,1:23:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（自由钟勒脖袭击）
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.10,1:23:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你经常出差？  - 哦，对，我到处跑\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- So you travel a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.48,1:23:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我旅行过一次\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, I travelled once.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.56,1:23:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…你是说你有60分钟时间还有大概60美元？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So, uh... you say you got about 60 minutes and about 60 dollars?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.44,1:23:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦不，我说过吗？  - 对，你说过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Oh, no. Did I say that? - Yeah, you did say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.31,1:23:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我想…大约20分钟和20美元，我就有这么多\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I think... about 20 minutes and about 20 dollars is what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.95,1:23:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天，太糟了，你没有40分钟和40美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gee, it's too bad you don't have about 40 minutes and about 40 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.91,1:23:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，糟糕，太糟了  - 对，真糟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, that's too bad. That's really too bad. - Yeah, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.25,1:23:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只有20分钟和20美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What I've got is about 20 minutes and about 20 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.84,1:23:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火车从不准点到，还老是这里那里地乱停\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know the trains are never coming on time. They always run away here and there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.35,1:23:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是臭名远扬，明白我意思吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They're notorious. Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.59,1:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打赌你至少有30分钟，至少\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I bet you at least got 30 minutes. At least.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.60,1:23:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我必须有30分钟吗？  - 至少30分钟\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Do I have to have 30 minutes? - At least 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.22,1:24:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，我相信我确实有30分钟和30美元\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, I believe I do have about 30 minutes and about 30 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.90,1:24:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我跟你说，我很快打个电话\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Great. I tell you what. I'll make a quick phone call...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.73,1:24:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约两分钟后在候车室后门见你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...and meet you in the back of the waiting room in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.67,1:24:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，你知道，那应该减2美元，不过…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, you know, that should be two dollars off but...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.54,1:24:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就放过你了，明白我意思吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}we'll let you go this time. Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.53,1:24:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不知道你的意思，你知道我的意思吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I don't know what you mean. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.70,1:24:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 再见  - 对，我知道你的意思\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- See ya. - Yeah. I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.58,1:24:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，拉尔菲\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, Ralphie.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.67,1:24:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得要20块\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I gotta have a 20.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.68,1:24:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欣赏你的木偶戏吧，多好的自由日\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just enjoy your puppet show. Have a good Liberty Day.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.16,1:25:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 慢点，啊，糟糕  - 你这快枪手水兵\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Slower. Aw, shit. - Some hotshot sailor you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.54,1:25:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是扯，你怎么不长大点学点东西，小水兵？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's ridiculous. Why don't you grow up and learn a thing or two, sailor boy?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.87,1:25:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在船上…给你10块，宝贝，10块\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I've been on a sh...Ten for you, baby. Ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.84,1:25:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，我的30块呢？他妈的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, what about my $30? You fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.54,1:25:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吹掉了，知道我的意思吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You blew it. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.34,1:25:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烂\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.33,1:28:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意，这是最后一次广播…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...Attention, please. This will be the last call...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.46,1:28:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开往匹兹堡和芝加哥的百老汇高级快车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...for the Broadway Limited to Pittsburgh and Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.68,1:28:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有全程前往芝加哥的乘客\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}All passengers travelling all the way to Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.64,1:28:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及4140车厢的中途乘客…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and passengers holding space in car 4140...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.79,1:29:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不觉得这事你有点过了吗？  - 我们没什么可失去的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Don't you think you're overdoin' this a little bit, do you? - We've got nothin' to lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.92,1:29:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我还有点理智，我应该拿起这东西扔进垃圾箱，就这样\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If I had any sense, I'd take this stuff and dump it in the trash, and that'd be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.25,1:29:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，但我还有原片在家里，所以…  - 所以为何这么做？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, but I got the original at home, so... - So why all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.22,1:29:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为曼尼的胶片，我跟你说过了，我们得小心处理\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Because of Manny's film. I told you. We gotta be careful with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.85,1:29:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道，我唯一真正惹上的麻烦，就是在我太过小心时\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, the only real trouble I ever got into was when I was too careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.23,1:29:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，调试音量，数到十，慢点\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Okay, give me a sound level. Count to 10, slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.44,1:29:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 一、二、三、四…  - 不，正常就好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- One, two, three, four... - No, just normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.69,1:29:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二、三、四、五、六、七、八、九、十\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.90,1:29:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好了  - 好了，咱们得赶快了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- All right. - Come on. We gotta get goin' here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.99,1:29:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 好，听着，不要忘了你戴着这个，明白  - 好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Okay, now look, don't forget you got this on, OK? - OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.66,1:29:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你需要我，跟我说话就行，你戴着话筒呢\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}If you need me, you just talk to me. You got that right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.16,1:29:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，肯定\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}OK. Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.08,1:29:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 莎莉，过来  - 什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Sally, come here. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.84,1:29:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.26,1:30:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通话完毕\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.36,1:30:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号月台，四号轨道，商旅特快车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Pay attention, state 3, track 4, Limited
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.56,1:31:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途停靠特伦顿、纽瓦克、纽约\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}stoping in Trenton, Newark, Newyork
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.23,1:31:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，杰克？能听见吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hello, Jack? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.53,1:31:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，就像我先前说的，关于去纽约之类\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, like I was saying before about goin' to New York and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.58,1:31:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以去看一些表演，比如…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}We could see some shows, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.45,1:31:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如“甜心宝宝”之类\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You know, like Sugar Babies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.22,1:31:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道时代广场有一家很棒的酒店…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}And I know a great hotel in the Times Square area...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.45,1:31:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sally?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.12,1:31:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨，我是弗兰克·唐纳休  - 哦，嗨，幸会\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Hi. I'm Frank Donahue. - Oh, hi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.29,1:31:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着，你不介意跟我走一会儿吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Litsen, would you mind walking with me for just a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.42,1:31:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 咱们去哪儿？ - 这个嘛…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}-Where are we goin'? - Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.22,1:31:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯…我觉得我们有点小麻烦  - 什么麻烦？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Well, I...I think we got a little problem. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.05,1:31:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很扯，但是…\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It sounds crazy but...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.09,1:31:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我们被跟踪了，对，没有疑问\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}I think we're being followed. Yeah. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.17,1:32:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天，你走太快了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}...Gee, you're a fast walker.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.98,1:32:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干我这行的，脚步必须快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Well, in my business you gotta be fast on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.01,1:32:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 杰克在哪？  - 哦，他在家休息\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Where's Jack? - Uh... Oh, he's at home, resting.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.63,1:32:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗯，压力是存在的  - 天，咱们要坐哪班火车？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Um, you know, the pressure can get to you. - Gee, which train are we takin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.89,1:32:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我还不知道，你带来录音带和胶片了？  - 对，就在我包里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I don't know yet. Got the tape and film? - Yeah, right here in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.59,1:32:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（往上层坡道  地铁）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.74,1:32:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想我们甩掉他了  - 对，再小心也不为过\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- I guess we lost him, huh? - Well, we can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.08,1:32:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.56,1:32:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不如走在我前面，慢慢走到月台尽头\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why don't you just walk slowly down to the end of the platform right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.96,1:32:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天，我不知道你为何觉得有人想跟踪我们\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Gee, you know, I don't know why you think anyone'd wanna follow us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.87,1:32:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人为了这种大新闻会干出的事情，会让你惊讶的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You'd be amazed what some people would do for a story like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.92,1:32:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，我想也是  - 别，不要转身\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, I guess so. - No, don't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.57,1:32:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 咱们可不能让自己暴露  - 对，没错\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- We don't wanna give ourselves away. - Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.78,1:32:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就装作…什么事都没有，好吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just pretend like nothing's happened, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.90,1:33:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看这地方，真恶心\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Just look at this place. This is disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.13,1:33:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，真是丢人  - 而且这里也不安全\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah. It's a real shame. - And it's not even safe any more, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.11,1:33:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它让我想起纽约那个人的事，记得那件事吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It reminds me of that story about that guy in New York. Remember that one?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.74,1:33:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得，我想我们写过一篇报道\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, I think we did a piece on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.31,1:33:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，他就是个高峰期搭乘地铁的人\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, his the guy who ride the subways at rush hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.79,1:33:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安安静静站在角落里，没人注意\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He'd stand in the corner real quiet so's nobody'd notice him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.50,1:33:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来他们进站了，他打开上衣抽出一把大切肉刀\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Then they'd pull in to a station, he'd open his coat and pull out a big meat cleaver,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.34,1:33:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用刀对着他们脑袋砍\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}and whack 'em right over the head with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.30,1:33:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 继续走，莎莉  - 好，后来他们举行了运输业罢工\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Let's go, Sally. - Yeah. And then they had this transit strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.39,1:33:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就消失了，就像是他也罢工了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}He just disappeared. It was like he went on strike too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.27,1:33:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不坐地铁\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's why I don't ride the subways.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.90,1:33:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安全，你知道，要不是因为你我连来都不来这里\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}It's just not safe. You know what I mean. I wouldn't even come down here if it wasn't for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.49,1:33:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续说，说啊\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, speak up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.36,1:33:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧，看到那个吓人的人了吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}You see what I mean? Do you see that creepy character?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.53,1:33:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所说的，这里再也不安全了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's what I'm talking about. It's just not safe any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.50,1:34:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，火车来了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The train's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.82,1:34:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富兰克林桥特快\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Franklin Bridge Express.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.82,1:34:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是咱们要去的地方吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is that where we're goin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.09,1:34:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪里？说啊  - 那是今晚他们放烟火的地方？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Where? Come on. - That where they're having the fireworks tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.76,1:34:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，你看，那里有家好酒吧\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}That's right. Listen, they got a nice bar down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.82,1:34:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们不如去喝一杯，聊聊天\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Why don't we have our drink and our little chat
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.22,1:34:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时欣赏一下烟花，你看如何？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}then take in the fireworks the sametime, what you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.72,1:34:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sure, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.31,1:34:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么你愿意帮我报道此事了？  - 好\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- So you like to help me cover the story? - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.00,1:34:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你可以给我们女性视角  - 对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- You could give us the woman's angle. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.15,1:34:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富兰克林桥特快，对吧？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Franklin Bridge Express, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.36,1:34:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，你干吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Hey, what you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.08,1:34:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉，莎莉\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Sally. Sally.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.21,1:34:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由日有什么大不了的？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}So what's the big deal with Liberty Day?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.48,1:34:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看过我们的相关报道吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Did you see our story about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.77,1:34:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没，我不看新闻，太压抑了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No, I don't watch news. It's too depressing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.33,1:36:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁去叫救护车\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Somebody get an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.17,1:36:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试后门\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Try that back door.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.75,1:37:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是16还是35？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Is it 16 or 35?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.00,1:37:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.82,1:37:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那卷胶片的规格\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}The gauge of the film.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.11,1:37:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台里只有16毫米的设备\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}They've only got 16mm equipment out at the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.19,1:37:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 对，我想就是那规格  - 不如你给我看一下\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Yeah, I think that's what it is. - Why don't you let me have a look?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.49,1:37:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦，当然  - 来，到亮光处来\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Oh, sure. - Here, come over into the light.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.92,1:37:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.67,1:37:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 录音带也在？  - 对\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}- Got the tape too? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.67,1:37:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，是16毫米的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Yeah, that's 16 all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.27,1:37:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要裹起来吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What are you... wrappin' it up?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.73,1:38:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干什么？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.03,1:38:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克会杀了你的\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Jack's gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.49,1:38:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，老天，不，不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Oh, God, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.88,1:38:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再出声你就死定了\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}One more sound and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.60,1:38:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧莎莉，咱们得报导烟火，记得吗？\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Come on, Sally. We're gonna cover the fireworks, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.63,1:39:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，求你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Jack, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.68,1:39:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，求你\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}Jack. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.18,1:39:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs10\1c&HB4DCFC&}No.
